                java.sql.Timestamp created,
                int lcols,
                java.lang.String stats)
        Creates a new statistics object with names for the table and the index specified for convenience.
        Parameters:
        id - statistics identifier
        indexId - index identifier
        indexName - index name (may be null)
        tableId - table identifier
        tableName - table name (may be null)
        created - creation timestamp
        lcols - number of leading columns
        stats - the statistics, as reported when doing getString on the column STATISTICS in SYS.SYSSTATISTICS (number of unique rows and total rows, for instance "numunique= 3 numrows= 3")
